*'''克維拉'''：船體、飛機、自行車輪胎、防彈衣、防彈頭盔、防護手套<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www2.dupont.com/Personal_Protection/en_US/products/kevlar/index.html |title=Kevlar® |accessdate=2011-08-21 |archive-date=2011-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816162655/http://www2.dupont.com/Personal_Protection/en_US/products/kevlar/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*'''諾梅克斯與Kermel'''：防火衣、防熱衣、防火頭盔、防熱頭盔

